  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> June 2, 2025</p>

  <p>This Privacy Policy describes how EchoPrime handles your data.</p>

  <h2>1. Personal Use Only</h2>
  <p>EchoPrime is a private AI assistant used solely by Wayne Martin. No other users are authorized or supported.</p>

  <h2>2. Data Collection</h2>
  <p>The App does not collect or store any personal data beyond what Wayne Martin personally inputs and stores for his own use.</p>

  <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>EchoPrime may interact with third-party services (such as Google APIs or AI tools) which are subject to their own privacy practices. No data is shared with these services unless required for functionality.</p>

  <h2>4. Security</h2>
  <p>EchoPrime does not transmit data to any external server unless explicitly configured to do so by the Developer. Local and cloud-based encryption practices are used to safeguard personal content.</p>

  <h2>5. Contact</h2>
  <p>For questions, contact: <a href="mailto:ghwinslow1700@hotmail.com">ghwinslow1700@hotmail.com</a></p>

